I just downloaded the latest CVS head version
(heritrix-1.1.0-200410221948.tar.gz).  Once extracted, I start up
heritrix the same way I always have using bin/heritrix.  When I log
into the wui though, I enter admin/letmein, and then it goes to a page
with:

HTTP ERROR: 404 Not Found

RequestURI=/favicon.ico

Powered by Jetty://

Also, the heritrix image/icon on the main login page shows as a broken
image link.

It looks like heritrix starts up fine:

Mon Oct 25 12:49:10 MDT 2004 Starting heritrix.
Mon Oct 25 18:49:11 GMT 2004 Heritrix 1.1.0-200410221948 is running.
Web console is at: http://dev3lt:8080
Web console login and password: admin/letmein

Did I forget something?  I don't remember doing much else to set up
besides downloading and extracting the files, other than chmod on the
heritrix startup script.

Thanks,
Rob.
